\begin_inset Formula $\left\langle \hat{B}\right\rangle =\left\langle \hat{a}_{1}\hat{b}_{1}\right\rangle +\left\langle \hat{a}_{1}\hat{b}_{2}\right\rangle +\left\langle \hat{a}_{2}\hat{b}_{1}\right\rangle -\left\langle \hat{a}_{2}\hat{b}_{2}\right\rangle $
\end_inset

.
 If one assumes local realism
