\begin_layout Standard
Consider now, the state 
\begin_inset Formula $\left|\psi\right\rangle =\left(\left|+-\right\rangle -\left|-+\right\rangle \right)/\sqrt{2}$
\end_inset

, where 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{\sigma}_{x}\left|\pm\right\rangle =\pm\left|\pm\right\rangle $
\end_inset

, and 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{\sigma}_{x,y,z}$
\end_inset

 are the Pauli matrices.
 Let 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{a}_{1}=\hat{\sigma}_{z}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{a}_{2}=\hat{\sigma}_{x}$
\end_inset

, while 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{b}_{1}=-\frac{\hat{\sigma}_{z}+\hat{\sigma}_{x}}{\sqrt{2}}$
\end_inset

