\begin_inset Formula $\hat{b}_{2}=\frac{\hat{\sigma}_{z}-\hat{\sigma}_{x}}{\sqrt{2}}$
\end_inset

.
 Upon evaluating 
\begin_inset Formula $\left\langle \hat{B}\right\rangle $
\end_inset

 using the rules of QM, one obtains 
\begin_inset Formula $\left\langle \hat{B}\right\rangle =2\sqrt{2}\nleq2$
\end_inset

.
